name: Pyi Framework
body:
# PyiFramework

Welcome, gentlemen, to the Pyi Framework. Astronauts, war heroes, Olympians -- none of these people have used the Pyi Framework, hell they don't even know what it is. But you do. Congratulations.

So, who is ready to make some websites?

For the record, this is our official page. We're releasing Pyi into the wild soon, but for now it's under wraps. Come back soon for more info.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
